<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>تَفْسِيرُ سُورَةِ الرَّحْمَن<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٤ص١٠٧:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: <span class="c3">{الشَّمْسُ وَالْقَمَرُ بِحُسْبَانٍ}</span> <span class="c4">[الرحمن: ٥]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ:</span> <span class="c2">«كَحُسْبَانِ الرَّحَى»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ غَيْرُهُ:</span> بِحِسَابٍ وَمَنَازِلَ لاَ يَعْدُوَانِهَا،<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">حُسْبَانٌ:</span> جَمَاعَةُ حِسَابٍ، مِثْلُ شِهَابٍ , وَشُهْبَانٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>